      "date": "2014-03-13 02:32:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/552fadc8-aa52-11e3-82b1-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  1 tests failed: conf-sanity.",
